snippet.title: How to Start Turning Ideas into Reality (WITHOUT EXPERIENCE OR MONEY)
snippet.description:
In this video, I show you how you can start turning ideas into reality. I believe that we need to ENCOURAGE ideas that stray from the norm. I want to help you bring your ideas to life. 

I built a webpage specifically to embrace turning ideas into reality. I know there are a lot of great ideas out there ready become part of the world. It's called www.thecommunitywebpage.com and you can bring your ideas to life over there. No coding experience is required, and you don't have to pay a cent. 

You send me your idea, and I will try to code it and put it up on the webpage. 

If you're a college student, entrepreneur or someone wanting to try something new I'd love to bring your ideas to life :) -
